reviewText: I loved how it had the old Indian ways I mean it portrayed their lifestyles as harsh they should be given a hell of a lot more respect than we give them my Dads cousins wife is a full blooded Indian so Ive got Cherokee running through my veins too! Im not hairless but Ive got very few hairs and I think its from my Indian herettage I also love the romance they gave us
My girlfriend and I have spent hours re watching this show, we love the clothes, cars, story lines, sex, and behind the scenes double and triple dealings.  Can't wait to get Season III.
Great Acting - great story and great set.  It's very addicting.  I look forward to the next season.  Great work.

This was purchased as a gift.  The person who received Boardwalk Empire was tickled
pink. They love this series and were very pleased to receive it.
